@startuml 03_完整通话流程
title 视频通话全景时序（按阶段分组）

autonumber
actor "调用方" as User
participant "RtcInit" as Rtc
participant "UseCase" as UC
participant "SSE Server" as SSE
participant "JanusClient" as JC
participant "WebSocket" as WS
participant "Janus Server" as Janus
participant "PeerConnection" as PC
participant "对端车机" as Peer

== 阶段 ① 呼叫发起：SSE 唤醒 ==
group ① SSE 唤醒（获取 Janus 连接参数）
  User -> Rtc : videoCall(cameraId)
  Rtc -> UC : requestVideoCall
  UC -> SSE : GET sseUrl?devicesUniqueId&forceNewToken
  note right of UC : Authorization 头 + cameraId
  SSE --> UC : STATUS_WAKE_UP\n(token, wss, randUser, hashId)
  UC -> UC : _remoteWakeup=true\n_addStubTrack
end

== 阶段 ② Janus 会话建立 ==
group ② 建立 Janus Session（WebSocket + create）
  UC -> JC : sendTask(JanusConnect)
  JC -> WS : connect(wssUrl + hashId)
  WS --> JC : onOpen
  JC -> Janus : create (token)
  Janus --> JC : sessionId
  JC -> JC : startKeepAliveTimer(10s)
  JC -> UC : onCreateSession
end

== 阶段 ③ 插件绑定与用户注册 ==
group ③ attach videocall 插件 + 注册用户名
  UC -> JC : attachPlugin(videocall)
  JC -> Janus : attach
  Janus --> JC : handleId
  JC -> UC : onAttached(handleId)
  UC --> Rtc : JanusInitialized
  UC -> JC : registerUser(localName)
  JC -> Janus : message{register}
  Janus --> JC : EVENT{registered}
  JC -> UC : handleVideoCallEvent(REGISTERED)
  UC --> Rtc : RegisteredEvent
  UC -> UC : _localRegistered=true
end

== 阶段 ④ 对端就绪 → 发起 WebRTC 协商 ==
group ④ SSE 通知对端注册 + 发 SDP Offer
  SSE --> UC : STATUS_REGISTERED\n(对端已注册)
  UC -> UC : _remoteRegistered=true
  UC -> UC : sendTask(JanusCall)
  UC -> PC : createOffer
  PC --> UC : sdp(offer)
  UC -> PC : setLocalDescription
  UC -> JC : call(handleId, offer, remoteName)
  JC -> Janus : message{call + jsep}
  Janus --> JC : EVENT{calling}
  UC --> Rtc : InCallingEvent
  UC -> UC : _startCallingTimeoutTask
  note right of UC : accOn=true → 35s\naccOn=false → 15s
end

== 阶段 ⑤ ICE Candidate 持续交换 ==
group ⑤ Trickle ICE（打洞候选逐条上报）
  PC -> JC : onIceCandidate (逐个)
  JC -> Janus : trickle(candidate)
  PC -> JC : onIceGatheringState=Complete
  JC -> Janus : trickle{completed:true}
end

== 阶段 ⑥ 对端接听 → SDP Answer ==
group ⑥ 对端 accept 并返回 answer
  Janus --> Peer : incomingcall:randUser1
  Peer --> Janus : accept + jsep(answer)
  Janus --> JC : EVENT{accepted} + jsep
  JC -> UC : handleVideoCallEvent(ACCEPTED)
  UC -> UC : _cancelCallingTimeoutTask
  UC -> PC : setRemoteDescription(answer)
  UC --> Rtc : Connecting
  UC -> UC : _startWebrtcTimeoutTask(8s)
end

== 阶段 ⑦ 媒体通道建立 ==
group ⑦ ICE 协商 + 远端流到达 + webrtcup
  PC -> PC : ICE 协商 (P2P / RELAY)
  PC --> UC : onTrack (video/audio)
  UC -> UC : remoteVideoMap[streamId]=Renderer
  UC --> Rtc : StreamOpen(streamId)
  Janus --> JC : webrtcup
  JC -> UC : onWebRTC
  UC --> Rtc : Connected(cameraId)
  Janus --> JC : media{receiving:true}
  JC -> UC : onMedia
  UC -> UC : _cancelWebrtcTimeoutTask
end

== 阶段 ⑧ 通话进行中 ==
group ⑧ DataChannel 业务消息 + KeepAlive 心跳
  note over UC, Peer
    · 业务 DataChannel（id=0, ordered）收发麦克风状态等消息
    · KeepAliveChannel（id=1, unordered）每 2s 心跳
    · 连续 10 次无应答 → 判 DisConnected(OTHER)
    · Janus Session 每 10s 发 keepalive 防回收
  end note
end
@enduml
